headline: Jeff York Returns as Paycom’s Chief Sales Officer
summary: OKLAHOMA CITY, January 23, 2026--Paycom Software, Inc. (NYSE: PAYC) ("Paycom"), a leading provider of comprehensive, cloud-based human capital management software, announced that Jeff York is returning to serve as chief sales officer (CSO), effective January 23, 2026. York previously served as CSO at Paycom from 2007 to 2021 and has since been serving as Paycom’s Leadership Strategist.
